tag name|||Hypha
tag jj|||Hypha is an immersive virtual reality story that takes you on a journey to cleanse Earth from human-made disasters by becoming a mushroom.From spore to mycelium, you can experience the life cycle of a mushroom to understand the importance of the Fungi Kingdom as the main bioremediation agent of Earth.DIRECTOR: Natalia Cabrera SCRIPTWRITERS: Natalia Cabrera, Juan Ferrer EXECUTIVE PRODUCER: Sebastián González PRODUCTION MANAGER: Juan Ferrer DIGITAL ART DIRECTOR: Javier Garay, Richard Lapham 3D DESIGNER AND ANIMATOR: Javier Garay Mena PROGRAMMER: Paola González Olea SOUND DESIGNER: Diego Aguilar VOICE ACTRESS: Trinidad Piriz MUSIC COMPOSER: Daniel Marabolí SCIENTIFIC ADVISOR: Fungi Foundation GRAPHIC DESIGNER: Rosario Ureta
